      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "Material properties (Ti-6Al-4V: E=114 GPa, yield stress=880 MPa, tangent modulus=1.1 GPa; UHMWPE: E=0.93 GPa) sourced from traceable coupon test data provided by DePuy Synthes. Screw geometry from certified CAD files with dimensional inspection reports. Boundary conditions (crosshead displacement rate, fixture stiffness) measured directly from test machine calibration records. Achieved level 3 reflects traceable, measured inputs with documented uncertainty bounds.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
