      "name": "Test samples",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories (FDA CDRH and DePuy Synthes). Screws from same production lot with documented dimensional inspection (OD tolerance ±0.03 mm, thread pitch verified). UHMWPE blocks from single vendor lot. Sample representativeness confirmed by dimensional measurement report. Achieved level 3 reflects multi-lab testing with documented sample characterization.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
