      "rationale": "Systematic mapping of experimental inputs to FEA model inputs documented in equivalency matrix. Measured fixture stiffness incorporated into FEA boundary conditions. Material properties used in FEA drawn from same lot as tested constructs. Crosshead displacement and reaction force measurement points replicated in model. Equivalency confirmed by sensitivity analysis showing < 2% QoI sensitivity to remaining input discrepancies. Achieved level 3.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
