      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison using E/uval metric per ASME V&V 20. For all three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm): E/uval < 1.96, confirming model predictions are statistically consistent with experimental data at 95% confidence. Force-displacement curves compared graphically and quantitatively. Inter-laboratory variability characterized and incorporated into uval. Achieved level 3 reflects formal statistical comparison with uncertainty-normalized error metric.",
