      "rationale": "Validation activities directly replicate the COU: same device design (non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw), same test standard (ASTM F1717), same loading mode (static compression-bending), same QoIs as used in regulatory submission. Multi-laboratory execution increases confidence in result generalizability. The validation scenario is not an analogue but a direct replication of the intended use scenario. Achieved level 3 reflects high fidelity between validation scenario and COU.",
